Brown paper bag commit
M    helpers/ub_compile

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r909 | ralesk@uhulinux.hu | 2009-03-29 19:51:15 +0200 (v, 29 márc 2009) | 15 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/helpers/ub_compile
   M /trunk/src/helpers/ub_install
   M /trunk/src/helpers/ub_makeinstall

CMake support fix:

M    helpers/ub_makeinstall
  * check in .. for CMakeLists.txt due to being called from build/
  
M    helpers/ub_install
  * separate build environment seems to be customary in the cmake world (and compulsory with kdelibs)
  
M    helpers/ub_compile
  * CMakeLists.txt takes priority over ./configure if exists
  * add KDE home dir
  * force sysconf dir to /etc
  * force prefix to /usr
  * separate build environment seems to be customary in the cmake world (and compulsory with kdelibs)

